	<div class="codesnippetright col-lg-5 col-md-5 col-xs-12">

		<h3 class="snippettitle">Check</h3>
		<p class="snippetdescription">Check and checkmate are an integral part of any chess game, and our app recognizes this dynamic. </p>
    <p class="snippetdescription">Our code loops through all opponent's pieces to determine if any piece can move to the king's position. Our back-end logic ensures that players can not move themselves into check and that other pieces must move to prevent check.</p>
	</div>



